-- Hochschild Mining, Minera Andes Agree on Settlement of Lawsuit Over Loan
-- Amanda Jordan
-- 2010-09-20T06:05:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/hochschild-mining-minera-andes-agree-on-settlement-of-lawsuit-over-loan.html

          
          
             Hochschild Mining Plc said it
signed an agreement with Minera Andes Inc. regarding a $65
million project-financing loan provided by Hochschild to the San
Jose gold and silver mine in Argentina.  
 The parties also agreed to restructure a 2004 shareholder
loan agreement pursuant to which Hochschild and Minera lent
about $50 million to the co-venture entity known as Minera Santa
Cruz.  
